Fungi stabilize connectivity in the lung and skin microbial ecosystems.

Tipton L(1)(2), Müller CL(3), Kurtz ZD(4), Huang L(5), Kleerup E(6), Morris 
A(7), Bonneau R(2)(3), Ghedin E(8)(9).

Author information:
(1)Department of Computational and Systems Biology, University of Pittsburgh 
School of Medicine, Pittsburgh, 15260, PA, USA.
(2)Center for Genomics and Systems Biology, New York University, New York, 
